room_title: Escape room "Paradox Alley" by Paradox Emporium in Bradley
room_description: In the wake of the recent disappearance of our boss, Mr. Darkwell, we invite anyone brave and willing enough to enter “Paradox Alley.”  We seek individuals that fancy themselves investigators and are calm under serious time constraints. Other information regarding your mission is top secret and will be granted on a need to know basis. Battles of wit and frustration are certainly to be expected.
